  <name>Quark</name>
  <summary>A terminal-aesthetic Matrix client</summary>

  <description>
    <p>
      Quark is a desktop Matrix client with a terminal aesthetic and vim-style
      navigation. Built with Tauri, it provides a fast, lightweight interface
      for Matrix chat with support for E2EE, emoji reactions, stickers, GIFs,
      and Spaces.
    </p>
  </description>

